quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,92,"On heЙ“ataa moЖґЖґere nden haa wiЕ‹toЙ—on e ko Й“uruЙ—on yiЙ—ude kon. Kala woo ko wiЕ‹tiЙ—on, pellet Alla no Anndi Й—um"
  3,93,"Kala Г±aametee laatino daganii-Й—um Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila en, si wanaa ko Israa'iila harminanno hoore-mun ado Tawreeta Jippaade. Maaku: \"Addee Tawreetaare nden janngon nde, si on laatiima goonguЙ“e"
  3,94,"Kala fefindiiЙ—o fenaande [dammbi] e Alla Й“aawo Й—um, ko Й“en Й—on woni tooГ±ooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,95,"Maaku: \"Alla goongii. Jokke diina Ibraahiima kan; ooГ±iika [gaa diinaaji mehre], o laatanooki jeyaaЙ—o e Й“en sirkooЙ“e"
  3,96,"Pellet, aranndu e Suudu waЙ—anaandu yimЙ“e Й“en, ko ndun wondu Bakkata; barkinaandu e peewal wonannde Winndere nden"
  3,97,"Ino e mayru Aayeeje Й“annguЙ—e : darorde Ibraahiima nden. Kala naatuЙ—o e mayru, o laatoo hooliiЙ—o. No woodani Alla e dow yimЙ“e Й“en hajjugol ka Suudu [hormaandu], wonannde on hattanЙ—o e mayru laawol. Kala on yedduЙ—o, pellet, Alla ko YonndiniiЙ—o e winndere nden"
  3,98,"Maaku: \"Hey mon yimЙ“e Defte, e ko yeddanton Aayeeje Alla Й—en, Alla ko SeediiЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  3,99,"Maaku: \"Hey mon yimЙ“e Defte, ko falotoЙ—on e laawol Alla ngol, on gomЙ—inЙ—o HiЙ—on Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГ±anЙ—e hara ko on seediiЙ“e! Alla wonaali WelsindiiЙ—o e ko golloton kon"
  3,100,"Hey mon gomЙ—imЙ“e, si on Й—oftike fedde e Й“en okkaaЙ“e Defte, Й“e ruttay on heeferЙ“e Й“aawo gomЙ—inal mon"
